title: Good Omens - Heaven Is A Place [a/c]
author: Scribdoodle
comment:
THIS IS SO NICE 
I LOVE HOW YOU SAID THAT THEIR HEAVEN IS WITH EACH OTHER FOR 3:11 MINUTES!! 
I loved the glitchy start and the placement of the lines like Michael's "You have to choose a side Aziraphale" and like the next scene shows the handhold with Adam and the Ineffable husbands.
this is so beautiful and I never expected to cry over Good Omens like this
YOU MADE A VIDEO ABOUT AZIRAPHALE X CROWLEY  WITH MY FAVOURITE SONG!!! This is everything, thank you for making my day!!
every video you post is so wonderful and thoughtful and this is no exception <3
Im glad you can still hear them talk. Thank you. ❤❤❤
description:
...for anyone who was looking for "heaven is a place on earth" this is not that song, i'm sorry! (though i hope you'll still give this a chance)

though, on that topic - didja know theres a gregorgian chant to 'heaven is a place on earth'? there is. that exists!
